{"tid":2299834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國環保署長押後訪台","createTime":"2020-11-25T04:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T05:13:18.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0512da321fcc362fb2a3f2deab8fdf4b1a3c766c","tid":2299834,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:59:24.000Z","msg":"美國環保署表示，署長惠勒原定訪問台灣的行程將會押後，原因是要優先處理迫切的國內事務，訪台行程已經延期。<br />\n<br />\n美國傳媒報道，惠勒原定在下月5日率團訪台，討論應對海洋垃圾等環保議題，但外界質疑他以包機方式訪台，花費太高，加上接近政權交接，時間上不太合適。<br />\n<br />\n台灣駐美代表蕭美琴對惠勒押後訪台表示惋惜，但強調台美環保領域合作仍會持續，歡迎未來繼續交流。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561772-20201125.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561772-20201125.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=9aba4609\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561772-20201125.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=964c8172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561772-20201125.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e98b7afff29a158263ee6d3590c25c7e462701ca","tid":2299834,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T05:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5758d260e635949f2d20e06109421a66c605e1eb","tid":2299834,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T05:08:03.000Z","msg":"台灣不如偷偷地重啟核彈project<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d845ce55ed92bda74280ff14c5721dfd93a090","tid":2299834,"uid":286897,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T05:09:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0949c2de8a8211bcd47048aa1e10b4bb758eee9","tid":2299834,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T05:10:55.000Z","msg":"可能人地真係唔得閒呢<img sr